  "author": "Guru Bin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Reggae sub-bass at 3,000 PSI. The hydrostatic compression is the dub compression — pressureAmt=0.85 means the note attacks and then surrenders to the weight of the water. The filterCutoff=300 places this in the mid-depth column: warm enough to feel in the chest, dark enough to be subterranean.",
